;SEQUENCE
AS A RESULT OF A CLONING ARTIFACT, AN ALANINE
HAS BEEN INSERTED BETWEEN THE FIRST RESIDUE 
MET AND THE SECOND RESIDUE ARG.  MET 1 IS NOT 
OBSERVED IN THE ELECTRON DENSITY, HENCE THE 
INSERTED ALA IS NUMBERED 1 IN THE ENTRY, WITH 
THE REST OF THE RESIDUES NUMBERED AS IN 
SWISSPROT ENTRY P00894.
